  ('optometrist-moex-00362', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-c33a0f9f', 'sub-optometrist-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列的檢測方法中，那一項與調節性內聚力／調節力比值（AC/Aratio）無關？', '["遮蓋測試（covertest）", "馮格雷夫測試（vonGraefetest）", "改良式托林頓測試（modifiedThoringtontest）", "固視偏差（Fixationdisparity）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "56b79c9a9e45", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8080996efa52", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0903", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視光學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
